{"tid":842141,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"點食先可以大隻啊啊啊","createTime":"2018-09-30T05:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T18:33:27.000Z","uid":146214,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1481869c25a07ceea3b0d3fb2861e9e190b8a375","tid":842141,"uid":146214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:24:25.000Z","msg":"玩咗健身都大半年，但係身形都無咩大改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不斷問身邊嘅師兄同朋友，佢哋都話我要食多啲。但係我自己覺得自己已經食好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係仍然無咩大進展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我就開始有飲奶粉嘅想法<br />\n<br />\n喺網上睇好多資訊，大概都分到兩種<br />\n一種係 gainer 要粗就呢隻<br />\n另一種係 whey 要線條就呢隻<br />\n網上就當然推薦排骨仔食 gainer啦，因為佢除左蛋白外，都有高碳水，易上磅，可以有力D上舉重D鐵。但後果係真係會肥，到時候真係「上磅」就唔好後悔<br />\n<br />\n另外就係 whey，因為佢純蛋白無其他食物成份（碳水、脂質）令身體可以注重肌肉構成。但缺點係成效會比較慢<br />\n<br />\n我當然明白飲奶粉做gym絕對無可能一步登天一兩個月就由瘦低變The Rock<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係細佬無呢個能力同時間食real food（時間梗本唔允許自己食四、五餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）所以先有咁嘅想法，唔想自己去完健身房拳頭都揸唔到嘅努力因為飲食問題而白費咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPs:63Kg 177高瘦撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54aea3054daa30cc467c334022a48c504ed22d5b","tid":842141,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T06:20:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c033853472428e957b99020d58e9ba53c27ea5d","tid":842141,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T06:50:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6f45a601116aba6b1553fbf5bd7ce8ca9f722ef","tid":842141,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T06:56:48.000Z","msg":"我自己一日三餐<br />\n<br />\n一餐1000kcal左右<br />\n<br />\n都係食三餐而已"},{"pid":"10f84f68600f2836db69d71700c9acce7535376a","tid":842141,"uid":173814,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T06:57:10.000Z","msg":"屌你出面咁多gym post自己爬下文都懶"},{"pid":"44280ec139902a308a52bc932d934efb33748ddb","tid":842141,"uid":67610,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:00:44.000Z","msg":"留名 185CM 60KG 瘦到仆街"},{"pid":"85fd45c1363791bb89792f6bab9fcbdc3e237238","tid":842141,"uid":66292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:04:19.000Z","msg":"做左gym接近一年 體重冇重過 但有大隻到<br />\n<br />\n利申 70kg 177cm 小肥底"},{"pid":"ee8c7c87a252fc4ae1aebd8137b5e296b18db55a","tid":842141,"uid":8500,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:06:57.000Z","msg":"CHING 對兩種粉D分析都幾獨到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8caf1d37f039fc321d3a2b9f6257be3b573d01","tid":842141,"uid":22138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喺網上睇好多資訊，大概都分到兩種<br />\n一種係 gainer 要粗就呢隻<br />\n另一種係 whey 要線條就呢隻<br />\n網上就當然推薦排骨仔食 gainer啦，因為佢除左蛋白外，都有高碳水，易上磅，可以有力D上舉重D鐵。<span style=\"color: red;\">但後果係真係會肥</span>，到時候真係「上磅」就唔好後悔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPs:63Kg 177高瘦撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦 你想去到比賽級數咩？你63kg可以肥得去邊 你食唔夠一日飲2次都上唔到磅啊我同你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ed5e5d43b2316b9cb3d0d0abec77fc5212b583","tid":842141,"uid":146214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff8caf1d37f039fc321d3a2b9f6257be3b573d01","tid":842141,"uid":22138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喺網上睇好多資訊